#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/guides/automation/cron_jobs_howto.md:89
msgid "If the automated, randomized times do not work well in [For Workstations above](#for-workstations), and the scheduled times in the [For Servers above](#for-servers), then you can create your own. In this example, we are assuming you are doing this as root. [see Assumptions](#assumptions) To do this, type the following:"
